cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a novel attack framework using a GAN model to generate non-constrained adversarial examples. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), cryptography and security (cs.CR), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
